\contentsline {paragraph}{\numberline {46.2.2.5}Lesson 5: Pattern 2: Reflection and Bias-Check Agent (source identity preserved in pattern registry) - supports quality review and never replaces accountable human judgment}{734}{paragraph.46.2.2.5}%
